Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.53,0:00:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.24,0:00:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么痛恨人类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么身边\N偏偏带着人类的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.65,0:00:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸跟邪见\N再加上小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎会发生什么大事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.05,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师加上珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:25.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:32.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:36.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:40.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:44.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:48.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:57.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:02.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:06.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.85,0:01:14.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:22.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:26.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:33.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:39.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.03,0:01:46.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了寻找失踪的奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.55,0:02:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不断朝着\N丑寅方向前进的这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也在寻找奈落的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第96话 邪见爷爷生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷\N小玲肚子快饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让小玲去找东西吃  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很烦耶  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想这座森林\N会有东西给你吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时先忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.23,0:02:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静一点行不行…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.70,0:02:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找一下就回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信他竟然会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把所有的东西都吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连最后一包\N大蒜味薯条也吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃你一两包薯条\N干嘛那么小气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我特地留下来\N想要拿去送给地念儿的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种口味你不是一向不吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道随便尝两口\N就会吃得停不下来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你说这下怎么办嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的地念儿是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你们还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次云母\N不小心中了奈落的瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而治好它的消毒药\N就是地念儿给的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.34,0:03:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰巧这次\N会经过地念儿住的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想过去看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道\N送人的礼物居然被偷吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么偷吃嘛真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这个地念儿也是个半妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不过他很善良\N而且待人很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和犬夜叉完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  既然送人的礼物吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆继续往前走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能拿到一些\N治疗瘴气的药
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以后着想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看还是过去一趟比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.91,0:04:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次云母的事\N我也想去谢谢人家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  大家就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于犬夜叉\N你想怎样随你便咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真是心胸狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个一定可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.83,0:04:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷真的好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒虫最猛胜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不马上给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光会留下一些没用的废物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近\N应该有最猛胜的巢穴才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我马上去找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个  毒虫的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔喔…嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一记  人头杖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些缠人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  还不能把头抬起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要保护小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道等等\N杀生丸少爷会怎么夸我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么还在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是得救啦  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果追过去看看的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  帮我拔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔出来没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…邪见爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气跟剧毒\N全都跑进我身体里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子我死定了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.06,0:07:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要知道\N我可不是为了你才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了杀生丸少爷才死的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.07,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知不知道\N有什么办法可以解毒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着解毒了  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟着杀生丸少爷这样到处游历
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.52,0:07:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得自己好幸福喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这次就这么死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这一生也算死而无憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我转告杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说我邪见会保佑他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路上平安无事顺顺利利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.61,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得一定要转告他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:07:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样看着邪见爷爷死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意帮你做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说些话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:13.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就拜托你看看咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷  你千万不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里一直向东走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会见到一个名叫\N“地念儿药草园”的药田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到那去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我采一些“千年草的果实”回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“千年草的果实”?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的想救爷爷\N那就快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果太阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕阳下山前  你还没有采到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“千年草的果实”回来救爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:09:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候\N最猛胜的剧毒会攻遍我全身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一定会没命了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会在\N太阳下山之前赶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会赶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿吽  再快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这里吗  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我想应该是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在这里没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉不是想怎样\N都随他便就可以了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点小事还在意那么久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起嘛  我刚刚说得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙老是这样\N连道歉都那么没诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股味道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落那些毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是一些\N专门扑火找死的夏虫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别动手  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有感觉到\N四魂之玉碎片在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也感觉不到就在附近耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有感觉到那些奈落的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些毒虫说不定\N打算飞回奈落身边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别杀它们\N跟在后面看看再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说可以\N指引我们找到奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀…杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只最猛胜是你杀的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最猛胜?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是这只毒虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是思考肤浅的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找奈落的线索一断
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后要找他简直难如登天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把话说在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这些毒虫自己突然死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么喜欢替自己狡辩\N你还是一样不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁喜欢帮自己狡辩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛\N犬夜叉说的都是真话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你给我让开一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟这小子多说无益
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我的心情不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要动起手来\N可不会像之前那样手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.98,0:11:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大话最好少说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N你才不要哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们两个\N别打了好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两兄弟还是一样感情不睦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿吽\N你在那边等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是药草园耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不会错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是个山姥妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.34,0:12:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我想见一下地念儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们家地念儿\N谁都不想见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地念儿在家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想来拜托他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟他要点千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个人中了剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果找不到千年草果实救他\N他就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里\N已经没有千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么躲在被子里不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出来不怕你见笑\N其实是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的地念儿是个半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半妖?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有时候会像现在这样\N变成一个普通人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏这孩子胆子又特别小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他变成人类的时候\N根本不想让人看见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不可以告诉我\N哪里可以采到千年草的果实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己可以去采
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年草的果实\N是用来解妖怪剧毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…你是想要救妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.84,0:13:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是\N看上那个妖怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么是看上妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  原来你还不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事慢慢你一定会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得当年我也跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆先别提这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很希望能救邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.92,0:13:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉不觉得这个小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟戈薇姑娘很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是那个姑娘呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是有那么点像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年草的果实\N就长在后山的山谷里头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里住着魑魅魍魉各种妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人类其实很难采得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等天黑之后\N我就可以恢复正常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等一等\N天黑之后我陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我那些草长什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己爬上去采
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟戈薇姑娘还真像耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想…一个人\N孤零零的死去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿吽  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:14:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我觉悟吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呸  我才不像你那么怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.59,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干嘛随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想要知道\N奈落的行踪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落就在丑寅方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说奈落最后的形迹\N是往那边移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这条线索就容易多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这条命暂时寄放一下\N犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别走  杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛要追奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放过他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  阿吽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.10,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.81,0:16:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿吽  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先帮我守着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去采千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.76,0:17:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的\N不希望再有其他人死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的\N不希望看见其他人死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷  不要死…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望再有人死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.91,0:19:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒性开始发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  太阳就快下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲是赶不及回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始觉得眼花了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是幻觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀…杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷  你不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?你说有个小姑娘\N来找过地念儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不晓得她是不是\N能平安的采到千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真替她担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒觉得她一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小姑娘\N跟戈薇姑娘很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说她跟戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信那位小姑娘\N一定比我强得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就像戈薇姑娘一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一颗温暖的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像太阳一样的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信等她长大之后\N一定也有一颗善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地念儿  你别再说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  地念儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你恐怕对戈薇有些误解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇这个人\N很令人意外的小心眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了吧  地念儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.51,0:20:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说她心胸狭窄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下  给我坐下…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:20:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  你终于醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  邪见爷爷\N你已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说\N连我…都一起死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷救了你\N还把你带回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错啊  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不能再麻烦\N杀生丸少爷咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.16,0:21:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.76,0:21:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过邪见爷爷  还好你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭什么啊  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:21:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.32,0:22:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很高兴\N大家又可以在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.65,0:23:37.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.50,0:22:15.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.72,0:22:24.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:34.22,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.52,0:22:44.22,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:49.20,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.50,0:22:54.12,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:23:01.52,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:08.07,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:12.25,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.65,0:23:19.50,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:29.52,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:41.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
